# PageSmith

PageSmith is an AI-powered Publishing Operating System.

Its purpose is to transform structured ideas into professional digital products through repeatable, human-guided workflows.

## Current Status

🚧 Alpha Development

## Vision

Build the world's most trusted publishing operating system.

## Project Structure

- docs/ — Documentation
- pagesmith-core/ — Core engine
- tests/ — Automated tests
- examples/ — Example projects
- scripts/ — Utility scripts
- assets/ — Images, icons and resources